# Analytics (optional). Set this to your GA4 measurement id to turn on tracking.
# Without it, no analytics script loads and all tracking is a no-op.
#
# 1. Create a free GA4 property at https://analytics.google.com (Admin → Data streams → Web)
# 2. Copy the Measurement ID (looks like G-XXXXXXXXXX)
# 3. Set it below (or in your host's env vars: Vercel/Netlify → Environment Variables)
# 4. Rebuild/redeploy.
#
# Events tracked: page_view (per route), game_complete (per daily game), share.
VITE_ANALYTICS_ID=
